            (corresponding to cascade 'groups'). Web coordinators have access to all mastheads.

            (April 2017) School and brochure groups do not exist yet. Until the new brochure
            layout is complete, users (except for web coordinators) are assumed to be in the
            "Schools and Colleges" group and can only select the side panel hero.
         -->
